</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Platforms like Semrush, Ahrefs, and <a href="/best/seo-automation-tools/">SEO automation tools</a> can pull keyword rankings, traffic data, backlink changes, and site health scores on a fixed schedule without manual work. They should handle all data aggregation and report assembly.</p>
<p>But the narrative section, the recommendations, the competitor context, and the budget justification require human judgment. Clients pay for interpretation, not data retrieval.</p>
